token_lists.title: VesselsGen-0 Crew Challenge- Crew Fenrir
token_lists.description:
Someone must seek out the deep ones and dragons.   This intrepid crew set out of from the colony to explore this new world and slay the dangers that threaten our future here. 

They are the generation of colonists born on this harsh planet and they're sick of letting "the landers" call the shots and win all the glory.   Swiping equipment left to collect dust in their parents' personal item lockers, they banded together to make a name for themselves and earn their own honor.  

What adventure await them?  What monsters lurk in the depths of the oceans and forests?  For them the unknown is the flame they cannot help but fly toward.  Godspeed Crew Fenrir!

Let your imagination guide you across the Apocalypse.
